abstract: For Barry Diller, there’s nothing like the real thing: The chief executive of IAC/InterActiveCorp shelled out $7.4 million on 120,000 more shares of Coca-Cola, according to a securities filing made public on Tuesday.
snippet: For Barry Diller, there’s nothing like the real thing: The chief executive of IAC/InterActiveCorp shelled out $7.4 million on 120,000 more shares of Coca-Cola, according to a securities filing made public on Tuesday.
lead_paragraph: For Barry Diller, it seems, there’s nothing like the real thing.
